WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.733 --> 00:00:04.366
Mr. Yang, I don't know what kind of deception he used

2
00:00:04.366 --> 00:00:06.433
Make you feel like they are VIPs

3
00:00:06.466 --> 00:00:10.366
But I know all too well what they are

4
00:00:10.366 --> 00:00:12.133
They are liars

5
00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:13.200
I'm not lying.

6
00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.200
I just gave them a lot of money.

7
00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:18.466
But their appetite is too great

8
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.966
So there was a conflict.

9
00:00:21.533 --> 00:00:24.000
Aren't you Lin's mother?

10
00:00:24.066 --> 00:00:25.300
Why do you say so?

11
00:00:25.300 --> 00:00:26.800
You don't know

12
00:00:26.866 --> 00:00:30.033
I was indeed his mother before today

13
00:00:30.066 --> 00:00:31.433
But after today

14
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:33.200
I am no longer his mother

15
00:00:41.266 --> 00:00:45.900
He wants to break off the mother-daughter relationship with you

16
00:00:46.266 --> 00:00:50.033
That's right, I don't deserve to be his daughter

17
00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:51.966
My family is poor

18
00:00:52.566 --> 00:00:55.266
From a small illness to a small illness

19
00:00:55.666 --> 00:00:57.433
I forgot a lot of money at home

20
00:00:58.333 --> 00:01:01.966
So he had nothing to do with me.

21
00:01:01.966 --> 00:01:03.700
You know it

22
00:01:05.066 --> 00:01:06.066
So

23
00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:09.866
You don't want your daughter anymore.

